OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: The full results
OL,5,FCounting has begun in the 2026 Senedd
OL,6,FElection, with all 16 of Wales'
OL,7,Fconstituencies in the process of
OL,8,Fcalculating and declaring six
OL,9,Fsuccessful candidates.
OL,11,FA new voting system, using the D'Hondt
OL,12,Fmethod, means that the results are
OL,13,Fsupposed to more proportionally
OL,14,Freflect the number of votes each party
OL,15,Freceives.
OL,17,FIt means that on polling day, people
OL,18,Fcast just one vote for the party or
OL,19,Findependent they wish to represent
OL,20,Fthem in the Senedd. Six individuals
OL,21,Fwill be elected per constituency.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
