OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: The full results
OL,5,FTo get an outright majority, a party
OL,6,Fwould need at least 49 seats overall.
OL,8,FLabour have been the only party in
OL,9,Fpower in Wales since devolution began,
OL,10,Fso any change to that status quo would
OL,11,Fbe historic.
OL,13,FBoth the Liberal Democrats and Reform
OL,14,FUK only had one Senedd Member in the
OL,15,Flast Welsh Parliament term. The Green
OL,16,FParty have never had an MS, so any
OL,17,Fseats would be a first for them.
OL,19,FThe full results for your constituency
OL,20,Fwill be updated below as they are
OL,21,Fannounced.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
