OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: The full results
OL,5,FFollowing the results, a new First
OL,6,FMinister will be chosen in the coming
OL,7,Fdays. This has to be done within 28
OL,8,Fdays of the election, so by 3 June.
OL,9,FThis may take place in the first
OL,10,Fmeeting of the new Welsh Parliament.
OL,12,FCandidates for the position are
OL,13,Fnominated by MSs - anyone can be
OL,14,Fnominated and members can put
OL,15,Fthemselves forwards.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
