OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: The full results
OL,5,FIf multiple names are put forward,
OL,6,Fsomeone must get more votes than all
OL,7,Fof the other candidates combined to be
OL,8,Fsuccessful. If no one achieves this,
OL,9,Fthe candidate with fewest votes is
OL,10,Fdiscounted and further votes are held
OL,11,Funtil one person does receive a
OL,12,Fmajority.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
